ClientResponses.Response: Hey, thank you for getting in touch with us. That's roast and ground coffee at the bottom of your cup and nothing to be alarmed by. We're proud to have added roast and ground coffee to our NESCAFÉ Gold Blend. Adding roast and ground coffee gives your cup of coffee a more intense aroma and richer flavour, whilst maintaining the same smoothness. The roast and ground coffee is ground 10 times finer to ensure every cup you drink gives you a enjoyable coffee experience. It's sad to hear you're not a fan but we value your feedback.

ClientResponses.Response: Hi, thanks very much for letting us know your thoughts on the new recipe. We really appreciate your feedback! The residue you can see at the bottom of your cup is micro ground coffee that was added to NESCAFÉ Gold Blend during the recent change. This is non-soluble coffee and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee!
